      <title>Banco BPM 将讨论 UniCredit 的 110 亿美元收购要约</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/banco-bpm-set-to-discuss-unicredit-s-11-billion-takeover-bid</link>
